name: Adjustable Chain Bra Straps
description:
A must have to add to your wardrobe. Designed for the ladies who like to be unique and different.
Light smooth and flexible. These bra straps are a unique and fashionable way to add flair to your casual wear and a bit of elegance to your more formal wear. The bra straps are constructed from a gold chain with metal bra clips on each end.
Chains on the back with lobster claw clasp makes these easy to adjust for a one size fits all. The straps can be used on most bras. The easiest bra to use is a convertible bra. Remove the existing straps and replace with your new ones. If your want to use a traditional bra all it takes is a little alteration. All you need is a little thread and a needle. If you cut the straps a either end, leaving about half an inch (enough material to make a small loop). Make a loop with the remaining material and sew the loop in place.
